	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=213776"><span id="Scholar">Barli</span></a><br /><b><span id="Scholar">Scholar</span></b><br /><span id="notbold">55 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Good [4.05]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>Here are a few suggestions for a tank.&nbsp;&nbsp;Please note that the highest point items were not always taken.  These combinations are obtainable with up to 760 points in any given dungeon.<br/><br/>Armor piece:<br/>Mir	760		Malevolent Breastplate of Suffering<br/>AC:63, Str:10, Dex:9, Wis:8, Int:8, HP:75, Mana:75, FR:9, DR:9, PR:9, type1,type2,type3 	War, Pal, Clr, Shd, Brd	Chest<br/><br/><b>Type 1 slot: </b><br/>Ruj	357	All	Peerless Sphere of Fortitude<br/>Lore, Sta:10 <br/><br/><b>Type 2 slot choices: </b><br/>Guk	510	Aug2	Magnetite Fragment of Fortitude<br/>Notlore, Sta:10, PR:5 <br/>-or-<br/>Mmc	510	Aug2	Tainted Soil of Battle Stance<br/>Str:7, Sta:7 <br/>-or-<br/>Mmc	510	Aug2	Eroded Soil of Tenacity<br/>HP:25 <br/><br/><b>Type 3 slot choices: </b><br/>Mir	760	Aug3	Ice Prism of Avoidance<br/>Lore, Mod:Dodge+8% <br/>-or-<br/>Mmc	510	Aug3	Gravestone of Aggression<br/>Lore, Effect:VengeanceIII <br/>-or-<br/>Tak	510	Aug3	Shiny Sandstone of Reconstruction<br/>Lore, Effect:Regeneration V (worn) <br/><br/>Can turn into this: (3 examples listed)<br/><br/>Malevolent Breastplate of Suffering (augmented)<br/>AC:63, Str:10, Sta:20, Dex:9, Wis:8, Int:8, HP:75, Mana:75, FR:9, DR:9, PR:14,<br/>Mod: Dodge +8% <br/><br/>-or-<br/><br/>Malevolent Breastplate of Suffering (augmented)<br/>AC:63, Str:17, Sta:17, Dex:9, Wis:8, Int:8, HP:75, Mana:75, FR:9, DR:9, PR:9,<br/>Effect: Vengeance III<br/><br/>-or-<br/><br/>Malevolent Breastplate of Suffering (augmented)<br/>AC:63, Str:10, Sta:10, Dex:9, Wis:8, Int:8, HP:100, Mana:75, FR:9, DR:9, PR:9,<br/>Effect: Regeneration V (worn)<br/><br/>Any of these combinations would be awesome.  Many more combos are possible but I like these 3 best personally.<br/><br/><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Jun  1 17:45:03 2004</em></p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />Barli Truebeard / Overlord / Kane Bayle / EQ<br/>Barlson / Conjurer-Alchemist / Befallen / EQ2</td></tr>
